"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-lifestyle-trending-olympians-swelter-without-air-conditioning-as-2024-paris-olympic-games-green-initiatives-fall-short-for-disgruntled-athletes-news-story-840b2c2d9cf75f52a992a72ce65c59c7\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Competitors have sweltered in the Olympic Village as the Paris 2024 organisers' move to reduce carbon emissions by initially not including air conditioners has backfired.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 49, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.244903593938912e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.77874873578448e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitors\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 11}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon emissions\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 111}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioners\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympic Games' goal to limit carbon emissions with self-cooling rooms that do not need air conditioning backfired this week after complaints mounted from competitors when the French capital was hit with a heatwave.\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.5908166155705847, \"rank\": 0.6897524241508675, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Olympic Games' goal\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 201}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon emissions\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"self-cooling rooms\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 251}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 285}, {\"ngram\": \"complaints\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 322}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"a heatwave\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organisers' original plans for a geothermal system that pipes cold water underneath the floors to keep the rooms six degrees cooler than the outside temperature fell short of countering temperatures upwards of 35C this week.\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The organisers' original plans\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"a geothermal system\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"cold water\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"the floors\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"the rooms\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"the outside temperature\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"temperatures\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While richer nations like Australia, the United States, Canada and Japan planned ahead by providing their competitors with portable air conditioning, other nations were left sweating in their accommodation.\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999931730463893, \"rank\": 6.746614301330668e-06, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999986715115212, \"rank\": 1.328470931243899e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999999581632, \"rank\": 3.586373810755671e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.584442027197351, \"rank\": 0.710497679780986, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"richer nations\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"their competitors\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"portable air conditioning\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"other nations\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"their accommodation\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic committee did cave in and ordered 2,500 air conditioning units at the start of the month, however many are still left boiling in the 7000-room Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.244903593938912e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic committee\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"2,500 air conditioning units\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"the month\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sky News Australia's Matt Cunningham, who has been reporting on the scene in Paris, told Andrew Bolt he did not envy many competitors struggling with the tough conditions.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky News Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merce_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.8904672653668816, \"rank\": 0.11169297578966719, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merce_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Merce_Cunningham\"}, {\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999997888608, \"rank\": 2.1113959746838225e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Bolt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"many competitors\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"the tough conditions\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You would not want to be some of those athletes at the Olympics Village,\\\" he told The Bolt Report on Tuesday evening.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those athletes\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics Village\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"The Bolt Report\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday evening\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of the bizarre things about this is games organisers have been all about being environmentally friendly and being on \\u2026 a social justice crusade.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bizarre things\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u2026 a social justice crusade\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The great twist here is that the people who are going to be in the rooms with no air conditioning are going to be those from the poorer countries.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The great twist\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"the rooms\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"no air conditioning\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"the poorer countries\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Australians and the United States, they have been able to bring in their own air conditioning, but a lot of those athletes, they come from poor nations (and) their countries have not been able to afford to do the same thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their own air conditioning\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"those athletes\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"poor nations\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"their countries\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokeswoman Anne Deschamps acknowledged competitor complaints and said she wanted to accommodate the needs of Olympians during the heat.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.77874873578448e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitor complaints\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"the needs\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have found a balance for the athlete's village long term responsibility for a model neighbourhood with all of the (green) innovations and our short-term responsibility to give to high performance athletes the best conditions,\\\" she said as reported in the Herald Sun.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a balance\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's village long term responsibility\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"a model neighbourhood\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"the (green) innovations\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"our short-term responsibility\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"high performance\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"the best conditions\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"the Herald Sun\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia prepared for the sweltering heat at the Olympics last year with the Australian Olympic Committee chief executive Matt Carroll telling The Daily Telegraph in November he appreciated the green initiative but emphasised the need to cater for the athletes during the competition.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_Prepared\", \"score\": 0.99985782037