 2575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not going for a picnic,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a picnic\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competitors from nations that did not bring their own A/C had to reserve an air conditioner ahead of time at their own expense, however the vast disparity between units and rooms has left many in the lurch.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitors\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"nations\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"their own A/C\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"an air conditioner\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"their own expense\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"the vast disparity\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2773}, {\"ngram\": \"units\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"rooms\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"the lurch\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swiss rower Celia Dupre took to TikTok with a litany of complaints about the Paris 2024 accommodation, taking particular issue with the boiling rooms.\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9993805884435688, \"rank\": 0.0006178143270264328, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 2839, \"end\": 2844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celia_Stewart\", \"score\": 0.9999987788422184, \"rank\": 1.0726890048693193e-06, \"text\": \"Celia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celia_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celia_Stewart\"}, {\"begin\": 2859, \"end\": 2865, \"title\"